text.tspan: Dette er en Brewolution all grain øl, der skulle ramme 5,1%
alkohol, EBC 81 og IBU 33. Nærighed med vand gjorde dog urten
lidt kraftigere end planlagt. Derfor er flasker med II, imodsætning
til I, tyndet en smule ved flaskning. Bør måske lagres 1 - 3
"It's not about something to hide, it's about something to lose." - "Extraordinary.
Reports appear to be true." - "But even if it did, it would not be a victory. Abandoning open
society for fear of terrorism is the only way to be defeated by it." - "Without Tor,
when you walk the streets of the internet, you're always watched." - @Snowden
